OKADONGA GUMBI
Beyisabisa indlela ebiwashaya ngayo amagoli iCape Town City ngaphambi komdlalo wayo weDStv Premiership ne-Orlando Pirates kodwa ishaye udaka e-Orlando Stadium, ifakwa uswazi luka 2-0 ngoLwesibili.
ICitizens iye kulo mdlalo imisila ibheke ezulwini ngemuva kokubhaxabula kanzima ngo 4-0 iBloemfontein Celtic ngempelasonto kodwa yafika umpompi wamagoli uvaliwe kwiBucs.

Ibe nenkinga nokho iBucs ngomzuzu ka-26 abadlali bayo oThabang Monare noSiphesihle Ndlovu beshayisana ngamakhanda balimazana. Kuke kwamiwa isikhashana besalashwa.
Kodwa bakwazile ukubuya baqhubeke nomdlalo, uNdlovu ubesebhandishwe ikhanda lonke. Ngemuva komzuzu ebuyile enkundleni, uMonare ungqofe ibhola qede wahlala phansi kwacaca ukuthi kumele akh

 icishe yalithola elesithathu ngasekuqaleni kwesiwombe sesibili, kodwa yahluleka ukuthi ibhola ligcine ngokuqabula inethi. ICity yiyo ebisaphethe umdlalo kodwa ifice ingekho indlela yokudlula odongeni lwasemuva lweBhakaBhaka.
Empeleni nje, yize beyihlasela iphindelela iCitizens kodwa beyigcina ingafikanga kuRichard Ofori obesezintini zeBucs. Eqinisweni nje, yiPirates eyakhe amathuba angcono esiwombeni sesibili futhi bekumele ilithole elesithathu.

NGIKHOKHA KANJANI?
Ingabe unentela engakhokhiwe? Udinga usizo ngokunquma ngokuthi kumele wenzeni noma kumele ushayele bani?
Abakhokhi ntela, bobabili abantu ngabodwana namabhizinisi, badingeka ukuthi bathobele ngokugcwele intela ngokuthumela ngesikhathi izimbuyiselo nezinkokhelo.
Kuzimo lapho abakhokhi ntela bangathobeli khona umthetho futhi banesikweletu esisele sentela, umnyango wokuphathwa kwezikweletu uzimisele ekusizeni amabhizinisi nabantu ukuthi bathobele umthetho ngokugcwele.
Uma ufuna ukwenza inkokhelo ku-SARS, kukhona izinketho ezithile isb. Ebhange, nge-eFiling, nge-EFT noma.
Ukuze uthole eminye imininingwane mayelana nezinketho zenkokhelo, chofoza lapha.
Uma udinga ukushintsha imininingwane yakho yokubhanga ungakwenza lokho:
- Ku-eFiling ye-eFiler yakho ebhalisiwe Ku-eFiling ye-eFiler yakho ebhalisiwe
- Ngokwakho kunoma yiliphi igatsha le-SARS uma ungabhalisile nge-eFiling, noma
- Uma ugcwalisa uphinde uthumele Imbuyiselo yakho Yentela Yemali Engenayo yabantu abangabodwana (i-ITR12).

Mayelana NATHI
Isungulwe ngo-2010, i-Shanghai JPS Medical Co., Ltd ibihlinzeka ngemikhiqizo yamazinyo kumakhasimende avela emazweni angaphezu kuka-80 nezifunda. Imikhiqizo yethu yamazinyo eyinhloko imishini yamazinyo efana nokulingiswa kwamazinyo, iyunithi yamazinyo ebekwe esihlalweni, iyunithi yamazinyo ephathekayo, i-compressor engenawoyela kawoyela, i-shuction motor, umshini we-X-ray kanye ne-autoclave, njll. Sihlinzeka ngezinto ezilahlwayo zamazinyo njenge
amakhithi okufakelwa, amabhibhu wamazinyo, iphepha le-crepe, njll.
I-CE yethu ne-ISO13485 zikhishwe yi-TUV, eJalimane. Njengozakwethu onokwethenjelwa nochwepheshe e-China, i-JPS Medical iyakwazi:
Ukukunikeza imikhiqizo yamazinyo enomqondo we-ONE STOP SOLUTION ukuze wonge isikhathi sakho, uqinisekise ikhwalithi, ulawule ukunikezwa okuzinzile futhi ulawule ubungozi.
Gxila ku-R & D ukuze uhlale ulethela imikhiqizo emisha nethuthukisiwe.
Yabelana ngawe anda ngamathuba ebhizinisi nolwazi.
Khetha umlingani ofanele, wenze ibhizinisi elifanele.

e ngemibala egqamile, imichilo ye-LED engenziwa ngendlela oyifisayo inikeza amathuba angapheli okwenza kube ngokwakho nokuzwakala.

qukayo nekhula ngokushesha embonini yokukhanyisa.Ngokuguquguquka kwayo, ukusebenza kahle kwamandla kanye nobuhle, imichilo ye-LED iguqule umklamo wokukhanyisa wangaphandle, inikela ngamathuba angapheli okuveza ubuciko nokukhanyisa okusebenzayo.Ngokuthuthuka kobuchwepheshe kanye nokuthuthukiswa kwamathrendi okuklama, ikusasa lemichilo yokukhanya ye-LED yangaphandle liqhakazile, elizokhanyisa izindawo emhlabeni wonke futhi linothise ulwazi lwabantu lwangaphandle.

Mayelana NATHI
Shanghai Shenyong Ngokukhethekile okuklama, ukukhiqizwa futhi yokuthengisa komugqa ngamakhasimende kagesi zempi ngocingo. Liphinde lunikeze uchungechunge namasevisi kumakhasimende ethu ezifana ukufakwa, kabusha, ukukhanda kokusiphakamisela imishini mechanical nokwenza umsebenzi wokuvuselela izakhiwo & ukukhanda kagesi imishini elawulwa, ukukhiqizwa futhi yokuthengisa kwezakhiwo, ibhizinisi Consulting, Isigaxa Bump, ukucutshungulwa-trailer izesekeli. Le nkampani emakethe ngamakhasimende kokubili ekhaya aphesheya kanye unikezwe Class Inhlangano yenkampani. It ngokukhethekile ukukhiqizwa umugqa kagesi ezokuxhumana based zempi ngocingo Hank oyi-knotting imikhiqizo elula inoveli chungechunge. Imikhiqizo yethu zisetshenziswa kakhulu zokuxhumana ngocingo, amandla inethiwekhi, gesi.
Sesitimela, futhi fiber-optic ikhebula. Imikhiqizo yethu kufanele izinga lokukhanya, kanzima machining, efakwe kalula futhi kwagezi okuyinto livumela bokuphakama ngawo olunye uhlobo kagesi ezokuxhumana zempi izibopho Angeke uqhathanise.

La uhlelo lokusebenza leselula le-amazon, etholakala kuze kube muva nje nge-Android, iOS ne-Windows, ingenye esetshenziswa kakhulu yibo bonke abasebenzisi ukuthenga nokuyithola ngesikhathi esifushane ekhaya. Kodwa-ke, sonke esine-smartphone ene-Microsoft operating system sinenkinga namuhla.
Futhi yilokho uhlelo lokusebenza luye lwanyamalala esitolo esisemthethweni seWindows, ngaphandle kokuthi iMicrosoft noma iAmazon inikeze incazelo esemthethweni ngayo. Abaningi bakhomba iphutha, kepha okwamanje wonke umuntu uqagela ngaphandle kokwazi isizathu esiqondile sale nhlangano exakile.
Umphumela osheshayo ngukuthi akekho umsebenzisi ongafaka uhlelo lwe-Amazon kudivayisi yakhe yeselula, ngaphandle kwalapho sisebenzisa isixhumanisi sokulanda esiqondile, ongasithola LAPHA.
Okwamanje Kumele silinde inkampani eholwa nguJeff Bezos ukuthi inikeze incazelo ngayo noma leyo eholwa nguSatya Nadella ukuthi ithathe izinyathelo. Sethemba ukuthi lezi zincazelo azidingeki futhi konke bekungumphumela wephutha, ngoba uma kungenjalo kungaba yinkinga kubasebenzisi abaningi uma singakwazanga ukulanda uhlelo lokusebenza kwesinye sezitolo ezithandwa kakhulu.
Vele, akekho umuntu ongakhathazeka uma ngabe isicelo usuvele usufakiwe, ngoba ngeke ube nenkinga yokufinyelela uhlelo ngoba seluqhubeka lusebenza ngaphandle kwenkinga, okungenani okwamanje.

- ‚ÄúUNowa wenze njalo; njengalokho uNkulunkulu emyalile wakwenza.‚Äù (Genesise 6:22). UNkulunkulu usinika umusa nathi, futhi ulindele ukuba siphen
... (509 chars skipped) ...

- UNkulunkulu wayengakakhohlwa. Ukuthi: ‚ÄúUNkulunkulu uyakhumbula‚Äù kusho ukuthi isikhathi esifanele sokwenza okuthile sasifikile (Genesise 19:29; 30:22; Eksodusi 2:24; 1S. 1:19).
- Lapho uzamcolo esephelile, uNowa wavula ifasitelo lomkhumbi (Genesise 8:6). Wathumela izinyoni ezithize ukuyobheka isimo somhlaba (Genesise 8:7-12). Wamethemba uNkulunkulu, futhi 
... (509 chars skipped) ...
ubonga, umnikelo wokushiswa (Genesise 8:20).
- Yize uMose engakhulumanga ngakho kuleyo ndimana, izilwane ababengazidla yilezo ezihlobile (Genesise 7:2; 8:20).

PVGIS24 ivumela ukulungiswa okungenamkhawulo kokulingiswa kwesivuno selanga
amapharamitha ngokuya ngemininingwane yephrojekthi, njengokuthambekela kwephaneli,
ama-orientation amaningi, noma izimo zesivuno ezihlukene. Lokhu kunikeza ngokungenakuqhathaniswa
ukuguquguquka konjiniyela nabaqambi.
Ubuchwepheshe be-PV
Eminyakeni engamashumi amabili edlule, ubuchwepheshe obuningi be-photovoltaic buye baba
ongavelele. PVGIS24 ibeka phambili amaphaneli e-silicon e-crystalline ngokuzenzakalelayo,
ezisetshenziswa kakhulu ekufakweni kophahla lwezindlu zokuhlala nezohwebo.
Okukhiphayo Kokulingisa
PVGIS24
ithuthukisa ukubonakala kwemiphumela ngokuyibonisa ngokushesha
ukukhiqizwa kwanyanga zonke nge-kWh njengamashadi amabha namaphesenti esifinyezweni
ithebula, okwenza ukutolikwa kwedatha kube lula.
CSV, JSON Export
Ezinye izinketho zedatha zibhekwa njengezingafaneleki kangako emalini engenamkhawulo yelanga
ukulingisa kususiwe phakathi PVGIS24 ukwenza lula ulwazi lomsebenzisi.
Ukubona ngeso lengqondo nokubikwa kwedatha yobuchwepheshe
Imiphumela yethulwa njengamagrafu namathebula ezobuchwepheshe anemininingwane,
lula ukuhlaziya ukusebenza kwesistimu ye-photovoltaic.
Idatha ingasetshenziselwa izibalo ze-ROI, ukuhlaziya kwezezimali,
kanye neziqhathaniso zesimo.

I-NOX-Ukunciphisa Amafutha / Amanzi-Emulsification
I-nitrogen oxides (CHAx) yaziwa ukuthi iyingozi ngokushesha empilweni yabantu kanye nemvelo. Imishini ye-diesel kanye ne-petroli yocingo ehamba phambili neyesitoreji inomthelela ikakhulukazi ku-NO emhlabeni jikelelex ukuphuma. Ukufakwa amandla kaphethiloli ngamanzi kuyindlela yokunciphisa i-NOx ukukhishwa kwezinjini. I-emulsification ye-ultrasonic iyindlela ephumelelayo yokwenza ama-emulsions amafutha amancane / amancane.
Izimoto namaloli, ama-a
... (2673 chars skipped) ... 
a ishear ephakeme, usayizi wezinhlayiya (= usayizi we-droplet) wesigaba sokuhlakazeka sincishisiwe. Ecincane ubukhulu bezinhlayiyana, ukusimama okungaphezu kwe-emulsion eyenziwe. Ukuzinza okungeziwe kungatholakala ngokusungulwa kwama-surfactants noma okuqinisekisiwe. Chofoza ku-graphic above ukubona imiphumela yesampula ye-emulsification ye-ultrasonic yamanzi angu-10% emajini ngamafutha (i-Velocite 3, i-Mobil Oil, i-Hamburg yaseJalimane). Lesi sifundo senziwa ngu U-Behrend no-Schubert (2000).

Ukuvimbela nokulawula ubhubhane, uLida uyasebenza.
I-Lida Group ibambisane ngokuphelele ne-Eighth Engineering Bureau yase-China Construction kanye ne-Jinan Airport futhi yaqeda iphrojekthi yokwakha yokuqinisekisa izindlu ukuze kuvinjwe futhi kulawulwe izindiza zamazwe ngamazwe e-Jinan Airport ngesikhathi esifushane.Le phrojekthi ihlanganisa indawo elinganiselwa ku-3,400 square metres.I-Lida Group ihlinzeka futhi ifake amayunithi angu-110 weizindlu ze-prefabnjengezindlu zamabhokisi kanyeizindlu ezakhiwe ngaphambilingephrojekthi, ekwazi ukuhlalisa abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 ngesikhathi esisodwa.
I-Lida Group yasungulwa ngo-1993, njengomkhiqizi ochwepheshile kanye nomthumeli kwamanye amazwe ophathelene nokuklama, ukukhiqizwa, ukufakwa, nokumaketha kokwakhiwa kobunjiniyela.
I-Lida Group izuze i-ISO9001, ISO14001, ISO45001, isitifiketi se-EU CE (EN1090) futhi yaphumelela ukuhlolwa kwe-SGS, TUV, kanye ne-BV.I-Lida Group ithole Iziqu Zekilasi Lesibili Lenkontileka Yomsebenzi Wokwakhiwa Kwensimbi Yezinkontileka kanye Neziqu Ezijwayelekile Zenkontileka Zobunjiniyela Bokwakha.
Imikhiqizo esemqoka ye-Lida Group iqukethe inani elikhulu leikamu labasebenzi, Izakhiwo zensimbi, i-LGS Villa,Indlu yesitsha, Indlu ye-Prefab nezinye izakhiwo ezihlanganisiwe.Kuze kube manje, imikhiqizo yethu isithunyelwe emazweni angaphezu kuka-145.
Isikhathi sokuthumela: Sep-28-2021

I-Hemodialysis igxila
Izici Main:
Izinga lekhwalithi ephezulu
Ukukhiqizwa okujwayelekile kwebanga lezokwelapha, ukulawula amabhaktheriya okuqinile, i-endotoxin nokuqukethwe kwensimbi esindayo, ukunciphisa ngempumelelo ukuvuvukala kwe-dialysis.
Izinga elizinzile, ukuhlushwa okunembile kwe-electrolyte, ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha kokusebenzisa imitholampilo nokwenza ngcono kakhulu ikhwalithi ye-dialysis.
‚óÜ Production imvelo isiqinisekiso
Iqhubekele phambili, i-GMP eqinisekisiwe i-100,000-level yokuhlanzwa i-workshop nendawo yokugcwalisa esezingeni le-10,000.
Ukuphepha kwenqubo yezobuchwepheshe
Umklamo wenqubo wenziwa ngokuhambisana ngokuqinile nezidingo zemijovo yezidakamizwa, futhi okulungiselela uketshezi okuzenzakalelayo kanye nemishini yokugcwalisa kusetshenziselwa ukuvimbela ukungcoliswa kwamagciwane.
Safety Ukuphepha kokuhlolwa kwekhwalithi
Kusukela ekuhlolweni okungenayo kwempahla eluhlaza kuya ekuhlolweni komkhiqizo oqediwe, sisebenzisa imishini yokuhlola eqondile ukulawula yonke inqubo yekhwalithi ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha komkhiqizo.
IHemodialysis igxilisa amamodeli nokucaciswa:
I-SXG-YA, SXG-YB, SXJ-YA, SXJ-YB, SXS-YA ne-SXS-YB

iphakethe lesiguli esimbili, iphakethe lesiguli esiphindwe kabili

UKHALELWE ngamaSongo kaSgonyela umsolwa oneminyaka ewu-28, obegqekeza ebrary Hertzog Park, eNewcastle, eNyakatho neKwaZulu-Natal. Kuvelile ukuthi umnikazi wendlu okugqekezwe kuyo ubone umnyango wendlu wangaphambili uvulekile, wabe esebona nokuthi umakhalekhukhwini wakhe sewuntshontshiwe, wabe esebikela amaphoyisa waboshwa khona lapho umsolwa, nomakhalekhukhwini obuntshontshiwe utholakele. Umsolwa usevelile eNkantolo kaMantshi waseNewcastle, kanti nophenyo lwamaphoyisa luyaqhubeka. Kwesinye isigameko kuboshwe umsolwa ngenkathi amaphoyisa abepatilola ephinde eseshe nabantu abasolisayo. Kuvelile ukuthi lamaphoyisa abehamba ku_Jordan Car Parking, esitaladini uVoortrekker ngenkathi ebona umsolwa ukuthi uphethe okuthize esandleni, okuthe uma ebona ukuthi amaphoyisa ayabona ukuthi uphethe okuthuza wabe esefumba isibhakela ngenhloso yokufihla lokhu abekuphethe. Kuphinde kwavela ukuthi lomsolwa ubephethe isikwama semali esincane okuthe uma amaphoyisa esithatha kuye athola umazisi, izincwadi zokushayela kanye namakhadi asebhange okungasiwona awakhe wabe eseboshwa khona lapho endaweni yesigameko. Kuphinde kwavela ukuthi umsolwa usevelile eNkantolo kaMantshi waseNewcastle ebhekene nalo lelicala lokutholakala nempahla yokwebiwa.
